Rar::getCrc

(PECL rar >= 0.1)

Rar::getCrc — Get CRC of the entry

Description

Rar
int getCrc ( void )

Rar::getCrc() returns CRC of the archive entry.

Return Values

Returns the CRC of the archive entry or FALSE on error.
